ra/TensorProduct/Defs.html#TensorProduct\">TensorProduct</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/RingTheory/LocalRing/ResidueField/Defs.html#IsLocalRing.ResidueField\">IsLocalRing.ResidueField</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">S</span>)</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">M</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Submonoid/Defs.html#Submonoid\">Submonoid</a> <span class=\"fn\">P</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/RingTheory/Localization/Defs.html#IsLocalization\">IsLocalization</a> <span class=\"fn\">M</span> <span class=\"fn\">S</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/RingTheory/FinitePresentation.html#Algebra.FinitePresentation\">FinitePresentation</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">P</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/RingTheory/Smooth/Basic.html#Algebra.FormallySmooth\">FormallySmooth</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span> <span class=\"fn\">S</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Let `(R, m, k)` be a local ring, `S` be a local `R`-algebra that is flat,\nessentially of finite presentation, and `k ⊗[R] S` is `k`-formally smooth.\nThen `S` is `R`-formally smooth.\n\nSince we don't have an \"essentially of finite presentation\" type class yet, we explicitly require a\n`P` that is of finite presentation over `R` and that `S` is a localization of it.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/RingTheory/Smooth/Fiber.html#Algebra.FormallySmooth.of_formallySmooth_residueField_tensor","kind":"theorem","line":141,"name":"Algebra.FormallySmooth.of_formallySmooth_residueField_tensor","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/RingTheory/Smooth/Fiber.lean#L141-L187"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.RingTheory.Etale.Field","Mathlib.RingTheory.Flat.Equalizer","Mathlib.RingTheory.Kaehler.TensorProduct","Mathlib.RingTheory.LocalRing.ResidueField.Fiber","Mathlib.RingTheory.Smooth.Local","Mathlib.RingTheory.Etale.Locus"],"instances":[],"name":"Mathlib.RingTheory.Smooth.Fiber"}